Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, Mash Burnedead!}Mash Burndead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Is it true that you can't use magic?}Mày không dùng được ma thuật hả?
