Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What about it, huh, Mash?}Sao thế Mash?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I can too.}Có chứ.
